						<li><a class="icons icon-icons_email-top-share tagmanager" title="Share by Email" href="mailto:?subject=Sharing a story from Hakai Magazine&body=I thought you might find this story interesting:%0D%0A%0D%0AGive a Village a Mangrove%0D%0ATo protect their mangrove forests and livelihoods, traditional communities in coastal Brazil set their hopes on small-scale tourism.%0D%0Ahttps://hakaimagazine.com/features/give-a-village-a-mangrove/" target="_blank"><span>Share by Email</span></a></li>



